         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Competitive procedure with negotiations for the purchase af a new playout platform</P>
            </TITLE>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="32210000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>This tender is for a replacement of the existing playout platform with a new fulfilling the following needs:</P>
               <P>— to support new functionality needed due to changes in the media landscape without compromising present quality and functional level,</P>
               <P>— to improve workflows in general,</P>
               <P>— to increase redundancy and minimise risk in relation to support and upgrades,</P>
               <P>— reducing the number of support hours needed to maintain and upgrade the system,</P>
               <P>— reducing the total cost including the cost for support contracts,</P>
               <P>— reducing the equipment count and complexity,</P>
               <P>— reducing the risk for hacking.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
